accessibility.text: Phyllis Harris is the Executive Director of the LGBT Center and has been an invaluable community partner on this project. Her enthusiasm is infectious and her and her \u2028team’s ability to convene a diverse set of \u2028voices has been a tremendous asset.

The LGBT Center of Cleveland is an integral part of the LGBT+ experience in Northeast Ohio and works every day to enrich the lives of the diverse LGBTQ community through advocacy, support, education, and celebration.
